title: Does anybody know what this is (and do you want to buy it)?
author: underwatersubmarine

comments.content: I'm not what they call a "trekie" however I believe that is what's known as a "Borg's Cube".
Looks like a coffee table cast in resin or some kind of engineered stone or concrete. A little chunky for my tastes.

Homage to wood type?

Miniature version of [the wall that Lou Dorfsman designed for CBS](http://web.archive.org/web/20131021031426/http:/www.underconsideration.com/speakup/archives/004496.html)?
